    "like_count": "2",
    "media_id": "17900000000000000",
    "parent_id": "18000000000000000",
    "text": "Jenna just sent this from the showroom floor. That lamp is NOT staying. Tell me you agree.",
    "timestamp": "2025-06-21T12:38:16+00:00",
    "user_id": "17841400000000002",
    "username": "karen"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "18000000000000001",
    "like_count": "16",
    "media_id": "17900000000000001",
    "parent_id": "18000000000000000",
    "text": "That piece would sell in a weekend at Bell Modern. Where'd you find it?",
    "timestamp": "2025-06-21T09:46:34+00:00",
    "user_id": "17841400000000003",
    "username": "dave"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "18000000000000002",
    "like_count": "5",
    "media_id": "17900000000000002",
    "parent_id": "18000000000000001",
    "text": "That's a keeper. Jenna's already asking if it'd sell in the showroom \u2014 Palm Springs buyers would snap that up.",
    "timestamp": "2025-06-19T21:34:23+00:00",
    "user_id": "17841400000000004",
    "username": "brian"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "18000000000000003",
    "like_count": "5",
    "media_id": "17900000000000003",
    "parent_id": "18000000000000002",
    "text": "That's Milo Baughman, not Dunbar \u2014 legs give it away. What's the ask?",
    "timestamp": "2025-06-20T18:31:20+00:00",
    "user_id": "17841400000000005",
    "username": "scott"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "18000000000000004",
    "like_count": "21",
    "media_id": "17900000000000000",
    "parent_id": "18000000000000003",
    "text": "That credenza is wrong for the space \u2014 too heavy. Pull it left by the Eames and send me another shot.",
    "timestamp": "2025-06-19T06:32:36+00:00",
    "user_id": "17841400000000006",
    "username": "jenna"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "18000000000000005",
    "like_count": "8",
    "media_id": "17900000000000001",
    "parent_id": "18000000000000004",
    "text": "That credenza Jenna sent \u2014 pass. Wrong patina for what we carry in Palm Springs. Who sourced it?",
    "timestamp": "2025-06-16T05:50:27+00:00",
    "user_id": "17841400000000007",
    "username": "megan"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "18000000000000006",
    "like_count": "9",
    "media_id": "17900000000000002",
    "parent_id": "18000000000000005",
    "text": "Adrian Pearsall sling chair, right? We had its twin on the floor last winter. Sold same week.",
    "timestamp": "2026-02-18T15:21:09+00:00",
    "user_id": "17841400000000008",
    "username": "rachel"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "18000000000000007",
    "like_count": "12",
    "media_id": "17900000000000003",
    "parent_id": "18000000000000006",
    "text": "The walnut grain on that is unreal. If you pass it, Bell Modern will take it \u2014 text Ashley first.",
    "timestamp": "2026-01-09T20:14:52+00:00",
    "user_id": "17841400000000009",
    "username": "tyler"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "18000000000000008",
    "like_count": "4",
    "media_id": "17900000000000000",
    "parent_id": "18000000000000004",
    "text": "Moved it left like Jenna said. Reads so much better next to the Eames now. Good call.",
    "timestamp": "2026-01-30T08:47:11+00:00",
    "user_id": "17841400000000010",
    "username": "priya"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "18000000000000009",
    "like_count": "18",
    "media_id": "17900000000000001",
    "parent_id": "18000000000000008",
    "text": "Hold it for me \u2014 I'll be in Palm Springs for Modernism Week and want first look at the showroom.",
    "timestamp": "2026-02-20T17:33:40+00:00",
    "user_id": "17841400000000011",
    "username": "marcus"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "18000000000000010",
    "like_count": "7",
    "media_id": "17900000000000002",
    "parent_id": "18000000000000009",
    "text": "Dunbar by Wormley, not Baughman \u2014 check the brass sabots. Either way it's a steal at that ask.",
    "timestamp": "2026-02-02T11:09:58+00:00",
    "user_id": "17841400000000012",
    "username": "linda"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "18000000000000011",
    "like_count": "3",
    "media_id": "17900000000000003",
    "parent_id": "18000000000000010",
    "text": "Dave's restoration on that bench is museum quality. Worth every penny of the showroom markup.",
    "timestamp": "2026-02-16T22:05:33+00:00",
    "user_id": "17841400000000013",
    "username": "omar"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "18000000000000012",
    "like_count": "11",
    "media_id": "17900000000000000",
    "parent_id": "18000000000000011",
    "text": "Is this still available? Saw it on the floor in Palm Springs last week and can't stop thinking about it.",
    "timestamp": "2026-01-25T13:42:19+00:00",
    "user_id": "17841400000000014",
    "username": "sofia"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "18000000000000013",
    "like_count": "6",
    "media_id": "17900000000000001",
    "parent_id": "18000000000000005",
    "text": "Megan's right on the patina. Refinish it and you kill the value \u2014 leave the original oil finish alone.",
    "timestamp": "2026-01-17T07:28:44+00:00",
    "user_id": "17841400000000015",
    "username": "derek"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "18000000000000014",
    "like_count": "14",
    "media_id": "17900000000000002",
    "parent_id": "18000000000000013",
    "text": "This is exactly the kind of piece that makes Bell Modern worth the drive from LA. Stunning sourcing.",
    "timestamp": "2026-02-24T19:56:02+00:00",
    "user_id": "17841400000000016",
    "username": "hannah"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "18000000000000015",
    "like_count": "2",
    "media_id": "17900000000000003",
    "parent_id": "18000000000000014",
    "text": "What's the depth on that? Need to know if it'll clear the alcove before I commit. DM me dimensions?",
    "timestamp": "2026-02-05T10:11:27+00:00",
    "user_id": "17841400000000017",
    "username": "nathan"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "18000000000000016",
    "like_count": "9",
    "media_id": "17900000000000016",
    "parent_id": "18000000000000015",
    "text": "That Noguchi table would sell before you get it fully staged. Put it by the window.",
    "timestamp": "2025-04-20T09:15:00+00:00",
    "user_id": "17841400000000009",
    "username": "tyler"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "18000000000000017",
    "like_count": "6",
    "media_id": "17900000000000018",
    "parent_id": "18000000000000016",
    "text": "Send me photos for an LA client \u2014 this is exactly their brief.",
    "timestamp": "2025-07-13T10:40:00+00:00",
    "user_id": "17841400000000007",
    "username": "megan"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "18000000000000018",
    "like_count": "14",
    "media_id": "17900000000000019",
    "parent_id": "18000000000000017",
    "text": "Glad the rosewood finish reads true in photos. Oil finish, six coats.",
    "timestamp": "2025-08-03T08:20:00+00:00",
    "user_id": "17841400000000003",
    "username": "dave"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "18000000000000019",
    "like_count": "5",
    "media_id": "17900000000000023",
    "parent_id": "18000000000000018",
    "text": "Already have two calls in about this one. Want me to hold it?",
    "timestamp": "2026-10-11T11:05:00+00:00",
    "user_id": "17841400000000006",
    "username": "jenna"
  }
]
